<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<title>Reset Your Password</title>
	<style>
		body {
			background-color: #f7f7f7;
			padding: 20px;
			margin: 0;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
		}

		.email-container {
			max-width: 800px;
			margin: auto;
			background: white;
			border-radius: 5px;
			overflow: hidden;
			border: 1px solid rgb(37, 99, 235);
			border-radius: 10px;
		}

		.header {
			background-color: rgb(37, 99, 235);
			text-align: center;
			border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
			padding: 10px;
		}

		.logo {
			max-height: 120px;
		}

		.email-content {
			padding: 30px;
			color: black;
		}

		.email-content h2 {
			text-align: center;
			color: black;
		}

		.email-content p {
			margin: 10px 0;
			color: black;
		}

		.button-table {
			margin: 20px auto;
		}

		
		.button-link  {
			text-decoration: none;
			background-color: rgb(37, 99, 235);
			color: #fff!important;
			padding: 12px 24px;
			font-size: 16px;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 5px;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
			margin: 15px;
		}
		
		.footer {
			padding: 20px;
			background: rgb(37, 99, 235);
			text-align: center;
			font-size: 12px;
			color: #fff!important;
			border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
		}

		.footer p {
			margin: 5px 0;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="email-container">
		<div class="header">
			<img src="cid:logo" alt="Company Logo" class="logo" />
		</div>
		<div class="email-content">
			<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
			<p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
			<p>
				You recently requested to reset your SmartBook account password. Click the button below
				to set a new password. This link is valid for the next 15 minutes.
			</p>
			<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center" class="button-table">
				<tr>
					<td align="center">
						<a href="<%= resetUrl %>" target="_blank" class="button-link">
							Reset Password
						</a>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
			<p>Thank you!<br />Team SmartBook</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<p>Copyright Â© 2025 SmartBook, All rights reserved.</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Our mailing address is:</strong><br />
				Sunshine Tower, 30th Floor, Senapati Bapat Marg,<br />
				Dadar West, Mumbai 400013, Maharashtra, India
			</p>
			<p><a href="#" style="color: #fff!important">Unsubscribe</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
